{
  "stem": "4247.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I wouldn't call it a surprise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was certainly a, a, a bad omen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We realized that, you know, the-- that's the beginning of the end.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We, we, we knew that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember when the first German tanks rolled into Ujpest, where I lived at the time, to, to Kiraly Street.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the, the local population received them warmly, the majority have.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were people-- this was very interesting from then on-- what was the local population's reaction.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Most people whose fortunes were attached to, to the ruling regime and, therefore, to Germany, naturally were barracking for Germany, right, because that was resulting in Hungary recovering some of the lost territory.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And their livelihood, you know, depended on that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so these people were barracking for, for the German and, by that time, the official Hungarian line.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I must admit that the official Hungarian line-- and if you read that book or part of it, you will see it very clearly from it-- varied in their degree of support to Germany.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, by that time we were occupied, by the-- Hungary was occupied by Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was no option but to toe the German line.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But because of the realization that it is-- by no means is it a foregone conclusion that Germany will won the war-- will win the war, some people in the governing circle started to look for options, right, for, for alternatives.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "However, speaking of the-- of the-- of the general public, which is-- that is interesting, the majority of that, as I said, were toeing the German line.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if it was at the expense of the Jews, so it-- so it be, right.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, we had some modest accumulated reserves, right?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
